               <p>THOMAS EDWARDS. On the 26th of May, about twelve o'clock in the day, I was on <placeName id="t18270531-116-crimeloc600">Tower-hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-116-crimeloc600" type="placeName" value="Tower-hill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270531-116-crimeloc600" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-116-off598 t18270531-116-crimeloc600"></join>, and stopped to look at some birds - I felt something at my coat-pocket, and missed my handkerchief, looked round, and saw she prisoner going towards the ditch; he sat down - I got through the rails to follow him; he saw me, got up, and ran - I called Stop thief! and saw him drop it - I took it up; he was stopped by an officer.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-116-person747">
